    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE

        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

2024-09-10 13:40:15.869 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r3]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r3].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r4].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r4]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r4].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r5]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r5].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r0].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

2024-09-10 14:03:15.281 +03:00 [INF] Request finished HTTP/2 GET https://localhost:44339/API/Categories/GetAllCategories - 200 267 application/json; charset=utf-8 1.9772ms
2024-09-10 14:03:15.284 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (11ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r3]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r3].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r4].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r4]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r4].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r5]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r5].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r0].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END DESC

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)

        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]

        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r5].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r0].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END DESC

    SELECT COUNT(*)

        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedAt] DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r3]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r3].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r4].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r4]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r4].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r5]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r5].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r0].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((

        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[OrderitemId]

    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN (

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE

        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((

        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]

    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]

        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0

    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]

    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]

        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r4].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r4]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r4].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r5]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r5].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END AS [Rating], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[DiscountPercentage], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId], [p].[ProductImage1], [p].[ProductImage2], [p].[ProductImage3], [p].[ProductImage4], [p].[ProductImage5], [p].[ProductImage6], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[Visiblity]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r0].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0
END DESC

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]

    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r1]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r1].[ProductId]) AS float) / CAST((

        FROM [Reviews] AS [r2]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r2].[ProductId]) AS float)
    ELSE 0.0E0

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]

    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]
        WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r0].[ProductId]) > 0 THEN CAST((

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = [r].[ProductId]) AS [ReviewCount], CASE
    WHEN (
        SELECT COUNT(*)
        FROM [Reviews] AS [r0]

        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([r1].[Rating]), 0)

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]

        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]

SELECT [t].[UserId], [t].[Address], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Email], [t].[FirstName], [t].[LastName], [t].[LoyaltyPoints], [t].[PasswordHash], [t].[PasswordSalt], [t].[passwword], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[Preferences], [t].[UserImage], [t].[userName], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[Address], [t0].[CreatedAt], [t0].[OrderDate], [t0].[ShippingStatus], [t0].[TotalAmount], [t0].[UserId], [t0].[VoucherId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[OrderId0], [t0].[PaymentDate], [t0].[PaymentGateway], [t0].[PaymentMethod], [t0].[Status], [t0].[TransactionID], [t0].[OrderitemId], [t0].[OrderId1], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[TotalPrice], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreatedAt0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductImage1], [t0].[ProductImage2], [t0].[ProductImage3], [t0].[ProductImage4], [t0].[ProductImage5], [t0].[ProductImage6], [t0].[ProductName], [t0].[StockQuantity], [t0].[Visiblity]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE [u].[userName] = @__principal_Identity_Name_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[LastName], [u].[LoyaltyPoints], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[passwword], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[Preferences], [u].[UserImage], [u].[userName]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[Address], [o].[CreatedAt], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ShippingStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [o].[VoucherId], [p].[PaymentID], [p].[Amount], [p].[OrderId] AS [OrderId0], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentGateway], [p].[PaymentMethod], [p].[Status], [p].[TransactionID], [t1].[OrderitemId], [t1].[OrderId] AS [OrderId1], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[Quantity], [t1].[TotalPrice], [t1].[ProductId0], [t1].[CategoryId], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ProductImage1], [t1].[ProductImage2], [t1].[ProductImage3], [t1].[ProductImage4], [t1].[ProductImage5], [t1].[ProductImage6], [t1].[ProductName], [t1].[StockQuantity], [t1].[Visiblity]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [o].[OrderId] = [p].[OrderId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[OrderitemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[CreatedAt], [p0].[Description], [p0].[DiscountPercentage], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage1], [p0].[ProductImage2], [p0].[ProductImage3], [p0].[ProductImage4], [p0].[ProductImage5], [p0].[ProductImage6], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[StockQuantity], [p0].[Visiblity]
        FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
        LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
    ) AS [t1] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t1].[OrderId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[UserId] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[PaymentID], [t0].[OrderitemId]
